      <title>Marvell 贏得新的 AI 晶片業務，但利潤率較低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/marvell-wins-new-ai-chip-business-lower-margins-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Marvell Technology 週四表示，已贏得新業務，幫助美國大型雲端運算公司生產人工智慧客製化晶片，但指出其客製化部門的利潤率低於其他業務部門。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/marvell-wins-new-ai-chip-business-lower-margins-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 17:05:39 GMT</pubDate>
