      <title>隨著 GenAI 競賽的升溫，亞馬遜任命人工智慧專家吳恩達 (Andrew Ng) 為董事會成員</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amazon-sees-opportunity-lower-costs-fulfillment-network-ceo-says-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亞馬遜週四將曾領導 Alphabet 旗下谷歌和中國百度人工智慧計畫的電腦科學家吳恩達 (Andrew Ng) 加入其董事會，原因是大型科技公司之間為增加 GenAI 產品用戶而展開的競爭日益激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amazon-sees-opportunity-lower-costs-fulfillment-network-ceo-says-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:41:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
